= SDL_Locale =
A structure that contains a preferred locale reported by the user



== Data Fields ==
{|
|const char*
|'''language'''
|a language name, e.g. "en" for English
|-
|const char*
|'''country'''
|a country, e.g. "US" for America; can be NULL
|}



== Version ==
This structure is available since SDL 2.0.14.

